    "body": "I think we have agreed before that inline should be the default backend when you use matplotlib inside an IPython kernel, but not got around to implementing it, because people are already used to running `%matplotlib inline`, and because it could be confusing if they've explicitly configured another default backend in matplotlibrc.\n"
