    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "You should still be able to configure it in `~/.ipython/profile_default/ipython_kernel_config.py`, by setting:\n\n``` python\nc.InteractiveShellApp.matplotlib = 'inline'\n```\n\nIt's an IPython kernel issue (because it's about executing Python code), so the config is there rather than under Jupyter.\n\nThanks for pointing out #6424 - I'll close this issue in favour of that one (and I'll actually get round to doing something about it).\n"
